ApplyPilot - Product Requirements Document (PRD)

Vision
Help job seekers spend less time searching and applying for jobs by using AI to discover opportunities, personalize applications, and automate repetitive tasks while keeping users in control.

Problem Statement
Job seekers spend hours searching across multiple job sites, reading repetitive descriptions, filling the same forms, uploading resumes repeatedly, and manually tracking applications.

Goal
Create an AI-powered assistant that finds matching jobs, personalizes resumes, generates cover letters, assists with applications on supported platforms, tracks applications, and saves time.

Target Users
Primary: Software Engineers, Designers, Product Managers, Marketing Professionals, Remote Job Seekers.
Secondary: Students, Fresh Graduates, Career Switchers, International Applicants.

Success Metrics
Jobs applied per user, interview rate, resume match score, time saved, DAU, WAU retention, premium conversion.

Core Features (MVP)
• User Profile
• AI Job Discovery
• AI Job Matching
• Resume Manager
• AI Resume Optimization
• AI Cover Letter Generator
• Job Dashboard
• Application Tracker
• AI Activity Feed
• AI Task Queue

Automation
Search jobs, open supported application pages, fill profile information, upload resumes, generate answers where appropriate, respect platform policies, and request confirmation where required.

Dashboard
Applications Today, Jobs Found, High Match Jobs, Interviews, Resume Score.

Search Filters
Location, Remote, Salary, Company, Experience, Skills, Job Type, Visa Sponsorship, Industry.

Analytics
Applications per day, response rate, interview rate, offer rate, top platforms, average match score.

Notifications
Notify users about matching jobs, review-required applications, recruiter responses, interview schedules, and resume optimization.

User Flow
Login → Create Profile → Upload Resume → Set Preferences → AI Finds Jobs → AI Scores Jobs → User Review (if needed) → Submit → Track.

Non-Functional Requirements
Fast dashboard, encrypted storage, secure authentication, HTTPS, queue-based processing, retries, monitoring.

Tech Stack
Frontend: Next.js, React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, TanStack Query.
Backend: Node.js, NestJS/Express.
Database: PostgreSQL + Drizzle ORM.
Auth: Supabase Auth/Clerk.
Storage: S3/Supabase.
Queue: Redis + BullMQ.
Automation: Playwright.
AI: OpenAI or Gemini.

Future Features
Chrome Extension, Recruiter Discovery, Referral Finder, Salary Benchmarking, Company Research, Email & Calendar Integration, Mobile App, AI Career Coach.

Risks
Automation restrictions, changing application forms, anti-bot protections, ensuring AI-generated content accurately reflects user qualifications.

MVP Scope
Included: Auth, Profile, Resume Upload, Job Discovery, AI Matching, Resume Optimization, Cover Letters, Tracker, Task Queue, Analytics.
Excluded: Mobile App, Interview Preparation, Recruiter CRM, Referral Marketplace, Team Features.

Product Vision
Build an AI-powered platform that helps users discover better opportunities, personalize applications, and dramatically reduce repetitive job application work.
